org.trippi.impl.base

Class SynchronizedTupleIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.trippi.TupleIterator
      • org.trippi.impl.base.SynchronizedTupleIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TrippiIterator<Map<String,org.jrdf.graph.Node>>

    public class SynchronizedTupleIterator
extends TupleIterator
    Wraps an TupleIterator and automatically releases the current thread's lock on the associated SynchronizedTriplestoreSession when closed.
    Author:
    cwilper@cs.cornell.edu
